name: SOL CAT
description: TODD is the cat that the Solana blockchain wants, and needs. TODD is here to bring together community with a playful twist. Within this community, we have been able to manage a friendly environment that everybody enjoys. We believe that is what crypto is about and what we prioritize as leaders in this community. With the help of CoinGecko, we can help spread this across the entire blockchain, which is our number 1 mission.
